ctions for strings and objects\n- RNG functions\n- Ranged cache\n- `List`, a class that combines the best aspects of `Set` and arrays\n- `JSONFileMap` and `FolderMap`\n- Version utilities\n- Xterm.js shell handling (arrows, home/end, prompting, etc.)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}